  { question: "How much rent should I budget for in Dubai?", answer: "A one-bedroom apartment in a popular area like Dubai Marina or JLT costs AED 6,000-9,000 (~€1,500-2,250) per month. More affordable areas like JVC and Sports City offer studios from AED 3,500 (~€875). Family villas in Arabian Ranches or Mirdif range from AED 12,000-25,000 (~€3,000-6,250). Most employers provide housing allowance." },
  { question: "Is Dubai safe for expat families?", answer: "Yes. Dubai is one of the safest cities globally, consistently ranking in the top 10 for personal safety. Crime rates are extremely low, police response is efficient, and family-friendly infrastructure is excellent. Schools, parks, hospitals, and entertainment venues cater well to families." },
